&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Identify and assess customers’ needs to achieve satisfaction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
