&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This role requires a self-starter who can shift seamlessly back and forth from their regular workload and ad hoc requests, without sacrificing analytical accuracy. The role also supports a period of significant organizational transformation and requires flexibility in balancing recurring responsibilities with evolving business needs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
